@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_bofygd(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = (0.66 - (wp.abs(tmp + 0.50) / v0))
    v1 = 0.87
    v0 = wp.cos((wp.exp(v2 + 0.93) / (v1 + 0.79 + tmp + 0.68)))
    v0 = wp.exp(wp.exp((tmp + 0.71 / tmp + 0.69)))
    v0 = 0.69
    tmp = v0
    v0 = ((v2 / v2) * ((v1 + 0.54 - v0 + 0.96) + v1))
    data[tid] = v0
